<blockquote class="gmail_quote" style="margin:0 0 0 .8ex;border-left:1px #ccc solid;padding-left:1ex">The error message indicates that libnuma was not installed on at least one node. That&#39;s a system library, not an OMPI one, so you&#39;ll need to get it installed by someone with root privileges.<br>


